Dapatkan pegangan, tetap tenang.

68
00:08:41.145 --> 00:08:42.438
Senang bertemu denganmu lagi.

69
00:08:44.023 --> 00:08:45.233
Tuan Do Ra-ik,

70
00:08:45.942 --> 00:08:48.444
