126
00:12:41.177 --> 00:12:42.887
-Bawa dia kembali!
-Bawa dia kembali!

127
00:12:42.970 --> 00:12:45.639
Jalankan Do Ra-ik!

128
00:12:45.723 --> 00:12:47.183
-Eksekusi dia!
-Eksekusi dia!

129
00:12:47.266 --> 00:12:49.643
Hidupkan kembali Kang Woo-seong!

130
00:12:51.061 --> 00:12:52.688
Setiap hari selalu seperti itu.

131
00:12:53.647 --> 00:12:55.983
Sampai saat ini,
Saya sibuk menarik penggemar

132
00:12:56.066 --> 00:12:58.652
